Templates for ICON Fortran codes
--------------------------------
- 'template_main.f90' is the base template for main programs.

- 'template_mo_module.f90' is the template for all new Fortran codes,
   which are not main programs. The module files are named mo_<name>.f90.

- If a module contains subroutines or functions, then these must be based 
  on 'template_subroutine.f90' or 'template_function.f90, respectively.

- Please note that "!>" and "!<" are part of Doxygen's syntax,
  and _not_ part of the <placeholder convention> used in templates.
